%H A123583 G. B. Shabat and I. A. Voevodskii, <a href="https://www.math.ias.edu/Voevodsky/files/files-annotated/Dropbox/Published%20versions/drawing_curves_published.pdf">Drawing curves over number fields</a>, The Grothendieck Festschift, vol. 3, Birkh√§user, 1990, 199-227.
